+```
+
+Forbidden in this phase:
+
+```text
+opening PostgreSQL connections
+executing SQL
+starting OpenRC
+creating Scheduler/EventBus instances
+publishing EventBus events
+calling GitHub API
+creating/upserting Qdrant collections or points
+adding non-stdlib dependencies
+```
